title: Laughing Through Life's Contradictions with Rachel Elizabeth
description:
Philosopher turned comedian Rachel Elizabeth was kind enough to sit down with me to share her story as to how she made her way to stand up. We speak on a variety of topics including freedom of speech in comedy.I had a wonderful time and Rachel made me laugh far too often, enjoy!

Listen to the podcast version here: https://anchor.fm/podcast-9b57fe4/episodes/Laughing-Through-Lifes-Contradictions-with-Rachel-Elizabeth-ejkl1u

Follow Rachel twitter: @feminist_th0t
Rachel's blog: https://rachelelizabeth.substack.com
Follow me on twitter here: @AndreaLynnLewis
email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
